annotationA: CG9149; acetyl-CoA C-acyltransferase activity. It is involved in the biological process described with: fatty acid beta-oxidation; Belongs to the thiolase family
annotationB: 3-hydroxy-3-methylglutaryl coenzyme A synthase; This enzyme condenses acetyl-CoA with acetoacetyl-CoA to form HMG-CoA, which is the substrate for HMG-CoA reductase
